Long-Term Safety and Efficacy of Epratuzumab in the Treatment of Moderate-to- 
Severe Systemic Lupus Erythematosus: Results From an Open-Label Extension Study.

Wallace DJ(1), Hobbs K(2), Clowse ME(3), Petri M(4), Strand V(5), Pike M(6), 
Merrill JT(7), Leszczyński P(8), Neuwelt CM(9), Jeka S(10), Houssiau F(11), 
